<i>noun</i>: 찬바람 [찬바람], 찬기 [찬기], 새침 [새침], 새치미 [새치미] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>찬바람 [찬바람]</dt><br>
<dd>coldness; cold wind</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 몹시 차갑고 싸늘한 기운이나 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) An energy or sensation that feels very cold and chilly.</dd><br>
<dt>찬기 [찬기]</dt><br>
<dd>1. chilly air; cold air</dd><br>
<dd>차가운 기운.</dd><br>
<dd>Cold air or a chill.</dd><br>
<dd>2. coldness; chill</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 정이 없고 차가운 분위기나 기운.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A state in which a person is cold and unkind, or such attitude.</dd><br>
<dt>새침 [새침]</dt><br>
<dd>cold attitude; coldness</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 관심이 없는 듯 조금 차가운 태도.</dd><br>
<dd>A slightly cold attitude as if one doesn't care about others.</dd><br>
<dt>새치미 [새치미]</dt><br>
<dd>cold attitude; coldness</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 관심이 없는 듯 조금 차가운 태도.</dd><br>
<dd>A slightly cold attitude as if one doesn't care about others.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>